{"tid":2348010,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"俾人叫Yellow Nazi/黃衛兵係有原因","createTime":"2020-12-31T12:08:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-31T17:29:58.000Z","uid":61861,"like":3,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5587f4434e683909e0986fc70879222c93b4a8a2","tid":2348010,"uid":61861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T12:08:47.000Z","msg":"我自己有subscribe 開奶茶、沙嗲牛麵、燒賣、常餐關注組，關注香港飲食文化，關注組亦係宣傳香港文化嘅一環！<br />\n<br />\n顧名思義關注組係關注果種食物，但係每當有人post 咗藍店出黎之後，永遠就會有人comment 一句「藍店不了」或者依家俾人鬧得多變咗做「難，不了」。<br />\n<br />\n藍店都可以好好食，只係唔想幫襯，我都唔會幫襯。我明白對於我地黎講一句藍店已經夠阻止我去食&hellip; 但出post者只係想邊度有好野食，佢問得已經証明咗佢唔會去查，你可以建議下同區有邊間（黃店）好食過佢，但一句「藍店不了」無助討論、無助黃色經濟圈增長、無助阻止藍店宣傳&hellip; 最後只會覺得黃屍on99，我都覺得個討論好戇尻。<br />\n<br />\n不服來辯"},{"pid":"9c443410c8dedcd544634e85f63ebe029ce89d51","tid":2348010,"uid":374209,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T12:10:01.000Z","msg":"沙嗲牛麵日日 好好運 屌你老母肯定收錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98a0f6c85ea1fcff40ab6f1e9fa87cd778f18728","tid":2348010,"uid":284432,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T12:14:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cf0e5ee701335d9fd3628fd0bfa8889b4683dff0","tid":2348010,"uid":311128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c443410c8dedcd544634e85f63ebe029ce89d51","tid":2348010,"uid":374209,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T12:10:01.000Z","msg":"沙嗲牛麵日日 好好運 屌你老母肯定收錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T12:15:12.000Z","msg":"之前有排一打開就係紅茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n兩間都未食過"},{"pid":"8d8b9f1673be7d4e88c50945dbba2c0707e2cd95","tid":2348010,"uid":6113,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T12:15:54.000Z","msg":"五毛 拉"},{"pid":"9dfbbdd201d4ad2737ea7afec3a